@node INSTALLATION "How to install"

INSTALATION
===========

Installation is very simple; just use the supplied Installer script.

You have only copy this line

@{B}YOUR_DISK(or ASSIGN):YOUR_PATH/accesdenide1.11@{UB}

every where in your startup-sequence...


@endnode

